window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Best-selling British master of science fiction Adrian Tchaikovsky brings listeners a new, mind-expanding science fantasia in <i>The Expert System's Brother</i>. </p> <p>After an unfortunate accident, Handry is forced to wander a world he doesn't understand, searching for meaning. He soon discovers that the life he thought he knew is far stranger than he could even possibly imagine. </p> <p>Can an unlikely savior provide the answers to the questions he barely comprehends?</p>"; 
